{"tid":1960871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"UFC 咀炮之王Conor McGregor譴責來自中國的劣質防護設備","createTime":"2020-04-06T11:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T12:00:42.000Z","uid":58552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e44057e47c6649ea3a26f84d6560bef20279e96d","tid":1960871,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"前UFC羽量級冠軍、輕量級冠軍Conor McGregor雖然被戲稱是格鬥界的嘴砲大師，不過他每次為家鄉愛爾蘭表態時，大砲性格往往備受推崇，McGregor近期不但拍攝了鼓舞人心的影片督促粉絲拳迷Stay Home之外，還批評了來自中國的防護設備補給品，認為它們是劣質的、可怕的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/thenotoriousmma/status/1246136172046422019?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthenotoriousmma%2Fstatus%2F1246136172046422019%3Fs%3D21&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=d0a12984\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthenotoriousmma%2Fstatus%2F1246136172046422019%3Fs%3D21&h=c185a701\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/thenotoriousmma/status/1246136172046422019?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nMcGregor會這麼說的原因，是因為愛爾蘭的衛生服務部長Paul Reid視察了這些來自中國的補給品之後，表示品質存在疑慮，引起了McGregor的憤怒，他也透過推特發文呼籲愛爾蘭不能依靠外界特別是來自中國的援助，而是要靠自己的力量站起來，「我們需要愛爾蘭自產的設備，我們昨天就需要了或者至少是西方國家製造的」McGregor這樣寫到，並且懇請大家有錢出錢有力出力去幫助前線的醫療人員。<br />\n<br />\n屌，究竟Tony 果場仲打唔撚打架"},{"pid":"b2c89f6b376be3ae96b33cb798c98530c5009b82","tid":1960871,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:59:36.000Z","msg":"Ireland都屌支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f5ea961ce132eb3fb29db3291cd54cb7a3dd9d","tid":1960871,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"風起了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}